Basic web sockets chat using erlang.

Requirements:
    Web browser with web sockets support
    Web server for serving static html (i.e. nginx)
    Erlang R14B02
    Rebar


Quick start:
    git clone git://github.com/nikolaeff/chatter.git
    cd chatter
    rebar get-deps compile generate
    sh ./rel/chatternode/bin/chatternode console

    Edit web socket url in html/index.html
    Point your web server to html/index.html
    Try to chat

It's full of bugs and should not be used in production.
